MarketMate is a web-based e-commerce platform that allows users to buy and sell products online. It is designed to provide a simple and accessible marketplace experience using modern web technologies and a database-driven backend.

This project was developed as an academic project and demonstrates full-stack web development, including front-end design, back-end logic, and database integration.

